<h1 >Additional features for hosts</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="c9f56aad-3c9f-4a39-b033-addfbd05e5cf" >

    <p>Additional features to help you manage your meeting room or make it more interactive.&nbsp;Please note that some features are turned off by default for privacy reasons or to minimize distractions in online lectures. </p> 
<p>You can review and enable any feature or settings by visiting your <a href="https://ryerson.zoom.us/profile/setting">Zoom's Settings page.<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a>&nbsp;If you have any questions about a specific feature, please contact <a href="mailto:avhelp@ryerson.ca">avhelp@ryerson.ca</a>.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#c9f56aad-3c9f-4a39-b033-addfbd05e5cf");});</script></div>

				

				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-opaque" id="133e251a-0674-40f8-937b-94d00daf1a99" >

    <p><strong>On this page:</strong></p> 
<ul> 
 <li><a href="#security">Security toolbar</a></li> 
 <li><a href="#engage">Increase engagement</a></li> 
 <li><a href="#screen-sharing">Screen sharing</a></li> 
 <li><a href="#co-host">Add a participant or teaching assistant as a co-host</a></li> 
 <li><a href="#virtual">Virtual background</a></li> 
 <li><a href="#cloud">Cloud recordings</a></li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#133e251a-0674-40f8-937b-94d00daf1a99");});</script></div>

				

				
