    <h2><a id="cloud"></a>Cloud recordings</h2> 
<p>When you record a meeting and choose&nbsp;<strong>Record to the Cloud;</strong>&nbsp;the video, audio, and chat text are recorded in the Zoom cloud.</p>
    





</div>
