	<div class="contentWrapper">
		<div class="iconContainer"><span aria-hidden='true' class='icon fa fa-exclamation-triangle'></span></div>
		<div class="textContainer"><h3>How to share recordings</h3> 
<p>Due to limited cloud storage, we ask that you&nbsp;download the files locally and&nbsp;delete it from the Zoom cloud, <strong>after</strong> the video and transcription has processed.&nbsp;We highly recommend uploading the Zoom recording to Google Drive instead. You can then share the Google Drive link by email or with D2L Brightspace. Learn&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/centre-for-excellence-in-learning-and-teaching/continuity-guide/share-audio-and-video-using-google-drive/">how to share audio and video using Google Drive.</a></p></div>
	</div>
